This paper is likely to belong to the cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) sub-category as it focuses on detecting malware capabilities. It also involves machine learning, which suggests it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The use of web technical documents from StackExchange suggests it could also belong to cs.SE (Software Engineering). Finally, the system described in the paper involves natural language processing, which could place it in the cs.PL (Programming Languages) sub-category.
